N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1500.9 - Conflicting rules deemed amended to conform

State Regulations

Any part of these rules which are in conflict with rules when
adopted by the committee on public access to records shall be deemed to be
amended to conform to such rules and to the statute. Notes
